01:02:03,780 --> 01:02:04,280
keys.
密钥。

1280
01:02:04,280 --> 01:02:07,312
If you've heard of RSA, Diffie-Hellman, elliptic curve cryptography,
如果你听说过 RSA、Diffie-Hellman、椭圆曲线加密，

